Clariant, a global specialty chemicals company, offers natural surfactants across a diverse range of applications, including personal care, household, and industrial products. The company's strong focus on sustainability and innovation has enabled it to stay competitive in the market by delivering high-quality surfactant solutions that meet customer expectations and regulatory standards.

